Docker Image commands
---------------------------------------

Image commands
1. To download a docker image
    docker pull image_name

2. To upload the Images
    docker push image_name

3. List of Images
    docker image ls
    OR 
    dokcer Images

4. To delete a docker image from docker host
    docker rmi image_name/image_id

5. To tag an image
    docker tag image_name ipaddress_od_local_registry:5000/image_name

6. To build an image from a customised container
    docker commit container_name/container_id new_image_name

7. To create an image from docker file
    docker build -t new_image_name

8. To search for a docker image
    Docker search image_name

9. to delete all images that are not attached to container
    docker system purne -a


